@startuml Sprint4_Sequence
autonumber
actor DPO
participant "Interface Web" as UI
participant "FastAPI" as API
participant "Orchestrateur\nLangGraph" as ORCH
participant "Agent A" as A
participant "Agent B" as B
participant "Agent C" as C
participant "Agent D" as D
database "SQLite" as DB

DPO -> UI: Soumettre une requete globale
UI -> API: POST /workflow
API -> ORCH: invoke(state initial)
ORCH -> A: Executer Agent A
A --> ORCH: Sortie A
ORCH -> B: Executer Agent B
B --> ORCH: Sortie B
ORCH -> C: Executer Agent C\nsi demande DSAR presente
C --> ORCH: Sortie C
ORCH -> D: Executer Agent D
D --> ORCH: Sortie D
ORCH -> DB: Sauvegarder traces,\nsnapshots et resultats
ORCH --> API: Reponse consolidee
API --> UI: Tableau de bord / synthese
UI --> DPO: Afficher vue globale

opt Consultation de l'historique
  DPO -> UI: Consulter traces ou snapshots
  UI -> API: GET /history ou /snapshots
  API -> DB: Charger l'historique
  DB --> API: Donnees historisees
  API --> UI: Historique restitue
end
@enduml
